itec.minicompiler.SymbolTable
Class Type

java.lang.Object
  itec.minicompiler.SymbolTable.Type
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArrayType, BasicType, RecordType
public abstract class Type
extends java.lang.Object

The Type implements a type a Symbol in the SymbolTable can have.

The Type is defined abstract so that the compatibility of two Types can be defined different for each Type.

Version:
1.0 (29.09.2004)
Author:
Stefan Leitner, Stefan Schauer
